<article class="padding-y-md">
    <div class="container max-width-adaptive-md">
        <div class="text-component line-height-lg v-space-md">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>

            <p>Please note that if you would like to report any bugs or glitches in our software, visit our <a
                    target="_blank" href="https://github.com/Mooonys">GitHub</a> page. You may also notify us with your suggestions
                via the <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/Mooonys/Mooonys/discussions">GitHub</a> page and/or our <a
                    target="_blank" href="{{URL 'collaboration/feedback'}}">Feedback</a> page.</p>

            <div class="text-divider"></div>

            <section id="email">
                <div
                    class="bg-contrast-lower radius-lg padding-top-md padding-bottom-md padding-left-md padding-right-md">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-xs">
                        <p class="color-contrast-high text-sm">
                            <i class="fas font-normal padding-sm fa-paper-plane"></i>
                        </p>
                        <blockquote><a target="_blank" href="mailto:contact-us@acolytes.de" class="color-primary">contact-us@acolytes.de</a></blockquote>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center gap-xxs">
                        <p class="color-contrast-high text-sm">
                            <i class="fas font-normal padding-sm fa-hands-helping"></i>
                        </p>
                        <blockquote><a target="_blank" href="mailto:help-me@acolytes.de" class="color-primary">help-me@acolytes.de</a></blockquote>
                    </div>

                    <div class="margin-top-xs bg radius-lg padding-y-sm padding-x-md">
                        <p class="color-contrast-higher text-sm padding-top-sm">
                            Please note that when contacting our support team there may be a delay as our support
                            team can be extremely busy so please be patient.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="text-divider"></div>

            <section id="address">
                <div
                    class="bg-contrast-lower radius-lg padding-top-md padding-bottom-md padding-left-md padding-right-xl">
                    <blockquote>
                        <p style="cursor: not-allowed;" class="noselect color-contrast-low">***************. **</p>
                        <p style="cursor: not-allowed;" class="noselect color-contrast-low">******-***********, *****</p>
                        <p style="cursor: not-allowed;" class="noselect color-contrast-low">*******</p>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="text-divider"></div>

            <p class="color-contrast-high">
                Are you still unsure about how to contact us?
            </p>

            <p>Find out more about how to contact us by <a class="color-primary" target="_blank" href="mailto:help-me@acolytes.de">sending
                    an email to our support team</a>.</p>

            <footer class="container margin-top-lg margin-bottom-lg">
                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="author margin-right-md author--meta">
                        <a href="#0" class="author__img-wrapper">
                            <img src="{{URL 'utils/img/jpg/me.jpg'}}" alt="Author picture">
                        </a>

                        <div class="author__content text-component v-space-xxs">
                            <h4 class="text-base"><a href="#0" rel="author">Reece Barker</a></h4>
                            <p class="text-sm color-contrast-medium"><time>Oct 15</time> &mdash; 2020</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <section id="signature">
                        {{> 2 width=164 height=164}}
                    </section>
                </div>
            </footer>
        </div>
    </div>
